{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 52,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الطُّورِ",
    "englishName": "At-Tur",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Mount",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 49,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4736,
        "text": "以山岳盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4737,
        "text": "以天經之書",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4738,
        "text": "寫於展開的皮紙者盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4739,
        "text": "以眾人朝覲的天房盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4740,
        "text": "以被升起的蒼穹盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4741,
        "text": "以汪洋的大海盟誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4742,
        "text": "你的主的刑罰，確是要實現的，",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4743,
        "text": "是任何人不能抵抗的。",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4744,
        "text": "在天體震動，",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4745,
        "text": "山岳逝去之日，",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4746,
        "text": "在那日，傷哉否認真理的人們，",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4747,
        "text": "即以妄言消遣的人們！",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4748,
        "text": "他們將被投入火獄。",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4749,
        "text": "這就是你們生前所否認的火刑。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4750,
        "text": "這是魔術呢？還是你們看不見呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4751,
        "text": "你們進火獄去吧！你們忍受其中的刑罰與否，隨你們的方便，那對於你們是一樣的。你們只受自己行為的報酬。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4752,
        "text": "敬畏的人們，必定在樂園和恩澤中，",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4753,
        "text": "他們因主的賞賜而快樂，他們的主使他們得免於烈火的刑罰。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4754,
        "text": "你們因自己的行為而愉快地吃喝吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4755,
        "text": "他們靠在分列成行的床上，我將以白皙的、美目的女子做他們的伴侶。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4756,
        "text": "自己信道，子孫也跟著信道者，我將使他們的子孫與他們同級，我不減少他們的善功一絲毫。每人應對自己的行為負責。",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4757,
        "text": "我將以他們所嗜好的水果和肉食供給他們，",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4758,
        "text": "他們在樂園中互遞（酒）杯，他們不因而出惡言，也不因而犯罪惡。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4759,
        "text": "他們的僮僕輪流著服侍他們，那些僮僕，好象藏在蚌殼裡的珍珠一樣。",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4760,
        "text": "於是他們大家走向前來互相談論。",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4761,
        "text": "他們將說：「以前我們為自己的家屬確是戰戰兢兢的，",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4762,
        "text": "但真主已施恩於我們，並使我們得免於毒風的刑罰。",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4763,
        "text": "以前我們的確常常祈禱他，他確是仁愛的，確是至慈的。」",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4764,
        "text": "你應當教誨眾人，因為借你的主的恩典，你不是一個占卜者，也不是一個瘋人。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4765,
        "text": "不然，他們說：「他是一個詩人，我們等待他遭逢厄運。」",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4766,
        "text": "你說：「你們等待吧！我確是與你們一同等待的。」",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4767,
        "text": "難道他們的理智命令他們說這句話嗎？不然，他們是放蕩的民眾。",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4768,
        "text": "難道他們說他曾捏造他嗎？不然，其實是他們不歸信。",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4769,
        "text": "叫他們作出象這樣的文辭來，如果他們是說實話的！",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4770,
        "text": "是他們從無到有被創造出來呢？還是他們自己就是創造者呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4771,
        "text": "難道他們曾創造天地嗎？不然，是他們不確信真主。",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4772,
        "text": "是你的主的庫藏歸他們掌管呢？還是他們是那些庫藏的監督呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4773,
        "text": "難道他們有一架天梯，可以登上去傾聽嗎？叫他們中的傾聽者拿一個明証來吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4774,
        "text": "難道真主有女兒，你們有兒子嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4775,
        "text": "難道你向他們索取報酬，故他們為納稅而擔負太重？",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4776,
        "text": "難道他們能知幽玄，故能將它記錄下來？",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4777,
        "text": "難道他們欲用計謀嗎？不信道者，將自中其計。",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4778,
        "text": "難道除真主外，他們還有別的神靈嗎？真主是超乎他們所用以配他的。",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4779,
        "text": "如果他們看見天掉下來一塊，他們將說：「這是成堆的雲彩。」",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4780,
        "text": "你任隨他們吧！直到他們遭遇自己被震死的日子。",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4781,
        "text": "在那日，他們的計謀，對於他們毫無裨益，他們也不受援助。",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4782,
        "text": "不義的人們，在那日之前，必定要受一種刑罰，但他們大半不知道。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4783,
        "text": "你應當忍受你的主的判決，因為你確是在我的眷顧之下的。你起來的時候，應當讚頌你的主；",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4784,
        "text": "在夜間和在星宿沒落之後，你應當讚頌他。",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
